Commentary Text: Rahul Chahar to Buttler, out Stumped!! Chahar responds beautifully after being nailed for six. This one's slower through the air at 85kph, teases Buttler into stepping out of his crease and then does him in the dip. Buttler isn't anywhere close to the pitch as he looks to slog. It turns past his outside edge and he's yards down the track leaving de Kock with an easy stumping. Buttler st de Kock b Rahul Chahar 41(32) [4s-3 6s-3]
